snippet.title: Ossuary - Satirical adventure game
snippet.description:
Ossuary is a pixelly, black-and-white-and-red game about talking to people and using sins as inventory items. It is available now for PC and Mac on various stores and will be available on Steam on May 27, 2015.

For more information, visit: http://fpgam.es/1L4kKgc

Ossuary is on Steam at: http://store.steampowered.com/app/363500/
